Did a little research... "Revolution Vol. 1" and "Revolution Vol. 2" are Tech's first two albums, "Point Of No Return" and "Bin Laden" are two subsequent singles, and the other three ("St1ll Revolutionary", "Portable Immortal" and "The Silenced Revolution") are unofficial fan compilations of live appearances, interviews, rare tracks, and collaborations.  IT's third official album will be entitled "The Middle Passage".
